name: Ay Guey Chicas Bien
overview: It tells the story of Susana (Alejandra Ambrosi) and Verónica (Vanessa Terkes), two girls who unexpectedly stumble upon a suitcase that contains 10 million dollars, and from that moment they are immersed in a singular flight, to escape the thugs chasing them to get their money back. In that escape, Susana and Verónica are confused with two wealthy heiresses, which will face them to a world totally unknown to them.
